title: Late night chorizo grilled cheese
description: I made a grilled cheese sandwich. The chorizo I keep in the freezer (along with a stick of pepperoni) so that I can grate it on a box grater and add flavor to fillings for things like grilled cheese, quesadillas, or pizza toppings. It's cooked on a Baking Steel Griddle and the tool is a mortaring trowel from home depot, which is my favorite press (and cheap!)
